minicoredumper (2.0.0-2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Require lsb-base >= 3.2-14 because reliance on /lib/lsb/init-functions
  * Limit packages to Linux
  * Fix build error on arch=x32 due to time_t with snprintf
  * Prevent co-installation with other core dumper handler, reported by
    Paul Wise, thanks (Closes: #846544)
  * Fix /var/crash permissions, reported and patch by Chris Lamb, thanks
    (Closes: #846588)

